{"tid":906514,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好心啲女人就唔好咁嘈啦，憑呢個例子就睇到，做女人係好好，女權社會","createTime":"2018-11-18T05:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T05:23:23.000Z","uid":150079,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0064e579737f7ad76f2e890467970be59cfc4dea","tid":906514,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:09:50.000Z","msg":"愛扮女人喜歡男性 跨性別港男：渴望被保護疼愛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/902593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/902593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我只係用以上例子作為一個論證<br />\n即係好似我咁我去日本呢個酒吧<br />\n屌你老味你又係人我又係人<br />\n我男人就要比3000<br />\n女人就比$500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本而家呢個世界就係女權社會<br />\n女仔揀男朋友嗰個機會係大過男仔揀女朋友<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然我哋已經溝到女啦，但係有時我都要去娛樂下咋嘛，我飲杯酒就貴過女人咩道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09955093665c2e88e32872f7be8d5c37632f3a3d","tid":906514,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:11:34.000Z","msg":"收佢3千<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9bb88bc01ac358fe71a18b98f2ecfa841a2766","tid":906514,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MxtcFT6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMxtcFT6.png&h=2f55e350&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db5b7f9e2e145e3d337c26b286759ffae246cc15","tid":906514,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09955093665c2e88e32872f7be8d5c37632f3a3d","tid":906514,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:11:34.000Z","msg":"收佢3千<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:15:58.000Z","msg":"我比3000yen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\